messages.message: Hey @sudeep - We are waiting for the IsBank team to Go-Live with their Cheque use cases (ETA- this week). Post that, we will start upgrading their envs. to the latest release.

Thanks all for the info!

Are we able to go ahead and disable the normal routine pipelines (per-language unit tests, certify (can do ad-hoc that's no biggie), systems/goldens, sandbox deployment, etc.?

JPMC Update -- i met with them today and they plan on deciding the exact version to upgrade by EOW, however, Q3 is when they plan on releasing it. They said "begin in August, complete by mid September". I had to explain to them what "no longer supportable" meant -- they thought it means they couldnt contact support :laughing: :eyes:
cc @amber

:joy:
Oh my
Why is this... sadly unsurprising :rolling_on_the_floor_laughing:
